Bowne to post $ 20 mln gain from unit sale . Bowne & Co Inc said Wednesday that it expects to post an after - tax gain of more than $ 20 million from the sale of its Baseline Financial Services Inc unit to Primark Corp . The $ 40 million cash acquisition was announced earlier today . The deal is expected to be consummated within 30 days . Bowne said Robert Patterson , Baseline ' s founder , will retain a 10 percent stake in the unit and will continue to manage the company under its new ownership . Baseline provides data and information products for investment managers . 
